<lb n="0756c13"/><head type="no">No. 493</head>
<lb n="0756c14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0756005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0756005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0756005"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿難四事經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0756c15"/>
<lb n="0756c16"/><byline type="Translator">吳<note n="0756006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月支國居士＝代【宋】【元】，優婆塞【明】，月支優婆塞【宮】</note><note n="0756006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月支國居士＝代【宋】【元】，＝優婆塞【明】，＝月支優婆塞【宮】</note><app n="0756006"><lem>月支國居士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">代</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">優婆塞</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">月支優婆塞</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0756c17"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在拘夷那竭國。欲滅度時。阿
<lb n="0756c18"/>難白佛言。我念天龍鬼神。帝<note n="0756007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0756007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝主【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0756007"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>人民與佛
<lb n="0756c19"/>相見。聞佛教誡。無不歡喜。在<note n="0756008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝心【三】</note><note n="0756008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志＝心【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0756008"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>所願。或
<lb n="0756c20"/>作沙門。得應真者。或有居家。奉行五戒。死
<lb n="0756c21"/>得<note n="0756009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（生）【三】</note><note n="0756009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上＋（生）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0756009"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">上生</rdg></app>天者。<note n="0756010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝念【宮】</note><app n="0756010"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>佛去世。天龍鬼神。帝王人
<lb n="0756c22"/>民。及四輩弟子。當何恃賴得福得度。將當
<lb n="0756c23"/>復從誰得之乎。佛言。善哉善哉。阿難。慈心多
<lb n="0756c24"/>愍天人雜類。無不由汝得度脫者。吾去之後。
<lb n="0756c25"/>世名五濁。人心憒憒。穢垢自亂。世多顛倒。
<lb n="0756c26"/>賤善<note n="0756011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尊＝貴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0756011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊＝貴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0756011"><lem>尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貴</rdg></app>惡。此實可憂。世雖然者。吾有經籍
<lb n="0756c27"/>懇惻之戒。盡心遵行。福自歸身汝莫憂也。吾
<lb n="0756c28"/>雖去世。典籍續存。六度大法不持之去。行
<lb n="0756c29"/>者得度非神授與。汝等不解吾之所言耶。阿
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0493.0757a" n="0757a"/>
<lb n="0757a01"/>難即白。願重說之</p>
<lb n="0757a02"/><p>佛言。大法有四。可從得福。亦可得道。<note n="0757001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（與得…當以）二十五字＝得福得道與侍（侍＝待【宋】）佛身正等難白佛為我解說四事佛言當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（與得…當以）二十五字＝得福得道與侍（侍＝待【宋】）佛身正等難白佛為我解說四事佛言當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757001"><lem>與得
<lb n="0757a03"/>佛身。其福正等。阿難又言。願佛為我解釋
<lb n="0757a04"/>四事。世尊曰。當以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">得福得道與待佛身正等難白佛為我解說四事佛言當</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得福得道與侍佛身正等難白佛為我解說四事佛言當</rdg></app>慈心育養幼弱。見禽獸蟲
<lb n="0757a05"/>蛾下賤仰人活者。常當愍念。隨其所食。令
<lb n="0757a06"/>得穌息。莫得加刀杖傷絕其命。惻愴慈心。當
<lb n="0757a07"/>如慈母天龍鬼神。帝<anchor id="fxT14p0757a01"/>王人民。有行此慈者。
<lb n="0757a08"/>其得大福。與侍佛身功德正等。此謂一事
<lb n="0757a09"/><note n="0757002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0757002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0757002"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。世有災異。水旱不調。五穀不豐。人民飢
<lb n="0757a10"/>饉。不安本土。志欲叛亡。王及臣民。富有倉
<lb n="0757a11"/>穀。當惟無常。身命難保。<note n="0757003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勿＝愚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勿＝愚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757003"><lem>勿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">愚</rdg></app>愛<note n="0757004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＋（重）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＋（重）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757004"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">寶重</rdg></app>穀。知愛
<lb n="0757a12"/>人命。當起悲心。出穀廩假。<note n="0757005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賙＝周【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賙＝周【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757005"><lem>賙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">周</rdg></app>諸窮乏。以濟
<lb n="0757a13"/>其命。安居本土。若意慳貪。不欲布施。當諦
<lb n="0757a14"/><note n="0757006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計＝忖【三】</note><note n="0757006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">計＝忖【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757006"><lem>計</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">忖</rdg></app>念。人初來生。魂神空來。依因<note n="0757007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝姻【三】，恩【宮】</note><note n="0757007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝姻【宋】【元】【明】，＝恩【宮】</note><app n="0757007"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">姻</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">恩</rdg></app>親情
<lb n="0757a15"/>欲之氣。以成己體。在母腹中。十月乃生。得
<lb n="0757a16"/>親喜悅。可得全命。愁忿之<note n="0757008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝曰【宋】【元】</note><app n="0757008"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>。即<note n="0757009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＝剋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切＝剋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757009"><lem>切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">剋</rdg></app>絕之。
<lb n="0757a17"/><note n="0757010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">困＝因【三】</note><note n="0757010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">困＝因【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757010"><lem>困</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>極乃終。魂神不滅。復更求身。豪貴貧賤。
<lb n="0757a18"/>皆由宿行。官爵俸祿。國土珍寶。無為迷惑。以
<lb n="0757a19"/>亂高德。至其壽終。身及珍寶。故留世間。不
<lb n="0757a20"/>隨己去。常當慈心練<note n="0757011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757011"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">存</rdg></app>經道。以佛明<note n="0757012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">教＝法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教＝法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757012"><lem>教</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>。觀
<lb n="0757a21"/>視人物。如幻如化。如夢如響。一切皆空。不
<lb n="0757a22"/>可久保。觀世皆爾。此為真諦。世人愚惑。心
<lb n="0757a23"/>存顛倒。自欺自誤。猶以金價。買<note n="0757013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00428;＝塗【宮】</note><app n="0757013"><lem>&CB00428;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">塗</rdg></app>銅也。身
<lb n="0757a24"/>死神去。當墮三塗。諦思如此。急當布施。與
<lb n="0757a25"/>身命競。貧窮乞&CB00456;。羸老疾病。隨所當<note n="0757014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757014"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0757a26"/>莫令<note n="0757015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝死【宮】</note><app n="0757015"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">死</rdg></app>絕。執心如此。十方諸佛。開士大人。
<lb n="0757a27"/>天龍鬼神。無不愍之。至於壽終。魂神所生。
<lb n="0757a28"/>輒受豪貴。身意俱安。災害不生。具獲上願。
<lb n="0757a29"/>如佛在時。供養佛身。正等無異。此謂二事
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0493.0757b" n="0757b"/>
<lb n="0757b01"/><note n="0757016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝世【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝世【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757016"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>。<note n="0757017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔國中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔國中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757017"><lem>國中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>多有盜賊。水火災異。變生毒氣。
<lb n="0757b02"/><note n="0757018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔流布〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔流布〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757018"><lem>流布</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>疾病縱橫。悉是海中龍神鬼王之所為
<lb n="0757b03"/><anchor id="fxT14p0757b01"/>也。故得此<note n="0757019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毒＋（氣）【三】</note><note n="0757019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毒＋（氣）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757019"><lem>毒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">毒氣</rdg></app>重病憂惱。此諸鬼神龍者。皆
<lb n="0757b04"/>是世人所為。射獵屠殺魚網。中毒死者。其魂
<lb n="0757b05"/>神或<note n="0757020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墮海中為龍＝海中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墮海中為龍＝海中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757020"><lem>墮海中為龍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">海中</rdg></app>。或為有力<note n="0757021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">太＝大【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">太＝大【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757021"><lem>太</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>神化生之
<lb n="0757b06"/>類。皆知宿命。忿怒宿怨。<note n="0757022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">因＝故【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因＝故【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757022"><lem>因</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>作霧露吐<note n="0757023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔惡〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757023"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0757b07"/>氣。雨其國<note n="0757024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＝土【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中＝土【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757024"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">土</rdg></app>。其時人民。或中毒死者。或但
<lb n="0757b08"/>得病者。有相塗<note n="0757025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔污〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔污〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757025"><lem>污</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>者。<note n="0757026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆由＝此皆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆由＝此皆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757026"><lem>皆由</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此皆</rdg></app>世人所作。不仁
<lb n="0757b09"/>殘殺物命。展轉相怨。<note n="0757027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手自＝自手【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手自＝自手【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757027"><lem>手自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自手</rdg></app>殺者。中毒即死。
<lb n="0757b10"/>助其喜者。皆更困病。或相塗污<note n="0757028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不相塗污〕－【宮】</note><app n="0757028"><lem>不相塗污</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b11"/>者。皆由食肉。有相分者。不相分者。<note n="0757029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聽聰＝聰明【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽聰＝聰明【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757029"><lem>聽聰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聰明</rdg></app>之
<lb n="0757b12"/>士。覺知殺罪<note n="0757030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">追＝遺【三】</note><note n="0757030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">追＝遺【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757030"><lem>追</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">遺</rdg></app>人不置。以己度彼。正等無
<lb n="0757b13"/>異。如此奉行。佛之弘道。行四等心。慈悲喜
<lb n="0757b14"/><note n="0757031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護＝捨【三】</note><note n="0757031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護＝捨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757031"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">捨</rdg></app>。福自歸身。若彼殺<note n="0757032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家＝害【宮】</note><app n="0757032"><lem>家</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">害</rdg></app>。以肉與己。慎莫
<lb n="0757b15"/>食之。不食<note n="0757033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝肉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝肉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757033"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">肉</rdg></app>者。雖處惡世。盜賊災變。毒氣
<lb n="0757b16"/>之時。雖處其中。不相塗染其帝<note n="0757034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【明】＊</note><app n="0757034"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>人民。<note n="0757035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">富＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">富＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757035"><lem>富</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b17"/>有盈穀。孤獨鰥寡。衣食不充。疾病困<note n="0757036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">篤＝苦【三】</note><note n="0757036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">篤＝苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757036"><lem>篤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>。無
<lb n="0757b18"/>以自濟。當給醫藥。糜粥消息。令其得愈。命
<lb n="0757b19"/>不橫盡。當明此人宿命行惡。不信三尊。背真
<lb n="0757b20"/>向偽。慳貪所致。罪福分明。慎莫為惡。亦當
<lb n="0757b21"/>慈心。以佛經法。教訓愚癡。令持經道。若<note n="0757037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">活＝治【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">活＝治【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757037"><lem>活</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">治</rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b22"/>一人。使病得愈。示之善道。<note n="0757038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝今【明】</note><app n="0757038"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">今</rdg></app>持五戒。終身
<lb n="0757b23"/>清潔。與侍佛身。其福正等。是謂三事<anchor id="fxT14p0757b02"/>也</p>
<lb n="0757b24"/><p>世有高節。清潔無欲。沙門梵志。懷抱經典。
<lb n="0757b25"/><note n="0757039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言輒＝輒言【三】</note><note n="0757039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言輒＝輒言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757039"><lem>言輒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">輒言</rdg></app>法律。帝<anchor id="fxT14p0757b03"/>王<note n="0757040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝人【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0757040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0757040"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民。心當恭肅。詣<note n="0757041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稟＝彼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稟＝彼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757041"><lem>稟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">彼</rdg></app>律
<lb n="0757b26"/>行。此曹高士。口之所陳。皆是諸佛<note n="0757042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之遺典也＝說之遺典【三】，之遺典【宮】</note><note n="0757042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之遺典也＝說之遺典【宋】【元】【明】，＝之遺典【宮】</note><app n="0757042"><lem>之遺典
<lb n="0757b27"/>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">說之遺典</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">之遺典</rdg></app>。令人去惡就善。恩倍於親。百有餘分。使
<lb n="0757b28"/>人壽終不墮三塗。常當慈心恭肅向之。寧<note n="0757043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洋＝烊【宮】</note><app n="0757043"><lem>洋</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">烊</rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b29"/>銅灌口。利刀截舌。慎莫謗毀此清潔之人。
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0493.0757c" n="0757c"/>
<lb n="0757c01"/>寧<note n="0757044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自斷手＝就斷首【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自斷手＝就斷首【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757044"><lem>自斷手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">就斷首</rdg></app>。莫加之痛。寧自<note n="0757045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剖＝割【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剖＝割【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757045"><lem>剖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">割</rdg></app>腹。出心燒
<lb n="0757c02"/>之。無怒此人。設使愚者見佛經道。明知去就。
<lb n="0757c03"/>由遠頑闇之<note n="0757046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">群＋（邪）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">群＋（邪）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757046"><lem>群</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">群邪</rdg></app>。馳就賢者之眾。講受聖典。
<lb n="0757c04"/>以成高德。沙門梵志。無以貿買求利為身穢
<lb n="0757c05"/>垢。心清行淨。猶明月珠。<note n="0757047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護＝故【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護＝故【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757047"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>持應器。勞身乞
<lb n="0757c06"/>食。供口即止。不畜遺餘。或居寺舍。或處山澤
<lb n="0757c07"/>樹下塚間。皆知宿命。分別真偽制作經籍。為
<lb n="0757c08"/>世橋梁。慈心多愍。坐起咒願。帝<anchor id="fxT14p0757c01"/>王<note n="0757048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝人【明】</note><app n="0757048"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民。令
<lb n="0757c09"/>國平夷。如此高士德訓。諸天龍鬼。惻心不
<lb n="0757c10"/><note n="0757049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">務＝豫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">務＝豫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757049"><lem>務</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">豫</rdg></app>世俗故。不為情欲之失所見歎述耳。國王
<lb n="0757c11"/><anchor id="fxT14p0757c02"/>臣民。若有<note n="0757050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757050"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>者。當尋求之。供所當得衣食
<lb n="0757c12"/>床臥<note n="0757051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾病＝病瘐【宮】</note><app n="0757051"><lem>疾病</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">病瘐</rdg></app>醫藥。使其安隱。得<note n="0757052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">講＝讚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">講＝讚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757052"><lem>講</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">讚</rdg></app>經戒。敷演
<lb n="0757c13"/>訓導。坐禪念定。或從得道。或死得上天。衣食
<lb n="0757c14"/>一國穢濁之人。不如盡心供養清淨道士一
<lb n="0757c15"/>人。其福弘大。如佛在時供養佛身。正等無異。
<lb n="0757c16"/>此<note n="0757053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝諸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謂＝諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757053"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>四事<anchor id="fxT14p0757c03"/>也。帝<anchor id="fxT14p0757c04"/>王<anchor id="fxT14p0757c05"/>臣民。<note n="0757054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視＝親【三】</note><note n="0757054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視＝親【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757054"><lem>視</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">親</rdg></app>此輩人。天
<lb n="0757c17"/>龍鬼神。無不擁護。助之歡喜<note n="0757055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者也〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757055"><lem>者也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0757c18"/><p>佛告阿難。吾前世時。行此四事。展轉受福。
<lb n="0757c19"/>自致得佛。吾以是故。重說四事。阿難。汝當
<lb n="0757c20"/><note n="0757056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔廣〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔廣〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757056"><lem>廣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為諸天帝<anchor id="fxT14p0757c06"/>王<anchor id="fxT14p0757c07"/>臣民說之。所作善行。自
<lb n="0757c21"/>得其福。終不唐捐。吾將滅度。四事<note n="0757057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（屬）＋累【三】</note><note n="0757057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（屬）＋累【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757057"><lem>累</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">屬累</rdg></app>汝。阿
<lb n="0757c22"/>難。聞經。且悲且喜。前以頭面。為佛作禮</p>
<lb n="0757c23"/><trailer><anchor id="fxT14p0757c08"/>佛說阿難四事經</trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
